<i>noun</i>: 주먹구구 [주먹꾸구], 경솔 [경솔], 경망 [경망] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>주먹구구 [주먹꾸구]</dt><br>
<dd>1. rough estimate</dd><br>
<dd>손가락으로 꼽아서 하는 셈.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of calculating by using fingers.</dd><br>
<dd>2. clumsiness; imprudence</dd><br>
<dd>어림짐작으로 대충하는 계산.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of calculating by taking a rough guess.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>경솔 [경솔]</dt><br>
<dd>thoughtlessness; hastiness; imprudence</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 조심성 없고 신중하지 못함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one's words or acts are careless and imprudent.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>경망 [경망]</dt><br>
<dd>flippancy; frivolity; carelessness; hastiness; imprudence</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 가볍고 조심스럽지 못함.</dd><br>
<dd>A remark or behavior being light and careless.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>